Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[denderedzwa]] (''circle'' kuEnglish) chiumbwa chine munyonya wakavharika panzvimbo dzose uye munyonga une nhambwe dzakaenzana panzvimbo dzose zvichibva pa'''goko''' (centre) re[[denderedzwa]] racho. Nhambwe iri pakati pe[[goko]] nemuganhu wedenderedzwa inodanwa kunzi [[nhara]], (radius kuEnglish).

==Nhambwe yemuganhu wedenderedzwa==
Muganhu we denderedzwa une nhambwe inopiwa ne[[tsazaniso]] inoti

[[Pimamuganhu]], P  =  2πR  = πD

Apa π i[[govano]] ye[[Pimamuganhu]] neDiameter ye[[Denderedzwa]], R ndiyo [[nhara]] yedenderedzwa, D ndiyo Diamater yedenderedzwa. Govano inonzi π, inoda kuyenzana na (22/7) kana kuti 3.14159 nekumwe kunyora.

==Nharaunda yeDenderedzwa==
Nharaunda rwuri mukati medenderedzwa runowanikwa ne[[tsazaniso]] inoti:

Nharaunda, A  = πR<sup>2</sup>  =  (πD<sup>4</sup>)/4

